rows.label: qev092710_MSG0020
rows.name:
Not long now. They'll be announcing
Hraesvelg's mass production soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0030
rows.name:
This model's really a cut above.
Can't wait for you to give it a spin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0045
rows.name: This isn't public knowledge yet, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0050
rows.name:
It's fitted with a special system.
Hraesvelg will blow other Skells right out of the water.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0060
rows.name:
It's still in development, but it really will
wow the pants off of you. Watch this space![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0080
rows.name:
Anytime you need a little extra help,
give me a call.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0090
rows.name:
I happen to be a pretty competent pilot.
That might be a skill you're in the market for.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0100
rows.name:
Before Grenada, Liesel was air force, and quite
the rising star. She made instructor in record time![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0110
rows.name:
I'd argue that she might even give the legendary hero
Alois Bernholt a run for his money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0120
rows.name: Okay now... That's laying it on a bit thick.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0130
rows.name:
In any case, I reckon we'd make a pretty
decent team in battle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092710_MSG0140
rows.name: After all, everyone could use an ace up their sleeve![ST:wait ]
